eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.EnergyAssessment
Energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: gross_eya_process (AssessmentProcessDescription): Specification of the model used to calculate the gross EYA estimates. gross_eya_results (list[Result]): Gross energy production predictions in GWh. plant_performance_loss_categories (list[PlantPerformanceCategory]): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. energy_uncertainty_categories (list[EnergyUncertaintyCategory]): Energy related uncertainty assessment categories including results. net_eya_results (list[Result]): Net energy production predictions in GWh, including overall uncertainties and results at different confidence levels.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_uncertainty.EnergyUncertaintyCategory
Category of an energy related uncertainty assessment.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceCategory
Plant performance loss assessment category.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss category. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. subcategories (list[PlantPerformanceSubcategory]): Plant performance loss assessment subcategories that fall under the category. The subcategory objects include details and results at the subcategory level. category_results (list[Result]): Plant performance assessment category result(s) as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.process_description.AssessmentProcessDescription
Description of a process used in an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the process or model. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.Result
Set of results for an element of an energy assessment.
Attributes: quantity (Optional[MeasurementQuantity(StrEnum)]): The quantity that the set of results describe, where this is not obvious from the context. Default is None. label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. assessment_period (Optional[AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)]): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is None. dimensions (Optional[tuple[ResultsDimension(StrEnum), ...]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceSubcategory
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceSubcategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance loss subcategory. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss subcategory assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the subcategory. variability (TimeVariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss subcategory. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss subcategory. Default is None. elements (Optional[list[PlantPerformanceSubcategoryElement]]): Plant performance loss assessment elements that fall under the subcategory. The element objects include details and results at the element level. A breakdown of plant performance loss subcategories into elements is optional and can be included only for a subset of the subcategories, as relevant. Whereas the categories and subcategories are fixed, the user may freely define element labels. Default is None. subcategory_results (list[Result]): Plant performance assessment subcategory result(s) as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.ResultStatistic
Result values for one specific statistic type.
Attributes: description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. statistic_type (StatisticType(StrEnum)): Type of statistic in the results component. values (UnionType[float, list[tuple[tuple[UnionType[float, int, str], ...], float]]]): Result as a single number or values at coordinates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.EyaDefDocument
IEC 61400-15-2 EYA DEF top-level data model.
Attributes: json_uri (Optional[str]): Unique URI of the JSON document. Default is None. title (str): Title of the energy assessment report. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. project_name (str): Name of the project under assessment. project_county (Alpha2CountryCode(StrEnum)): The ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 two-letter country code of the country where the project under assessment is located. document_id (Optional[str]): The ID of the report document; not including the version when 'document_version' is used. Default is None. document_version (Optional[str]): Version of the report document, also known as revision. Default is None. issue_date (date): Report issue date in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD. contributors (list[ReportContributor]): List of report contributors (e.g. author and verifier) issuing_organisations (list[Organisation]): The organisation(s) issuing the report (e.g. consultant). receiving_organisations (Optional[list[Organisation]]): The organisation(s) receiving the report (e.g. client), if relevant. Default is None. contract_reference (Optional[str]): Reference to contract between the issuing and receiving organisations that governs the energy yield assessment. Default is None. confidentiality_classification (Optional[str]): Confidentiality classification of the report. Default is None. coordinate_reference_system (CoordinateReferenceSystem): Coordinate reference system used for all location data. measurement_stations (Optional[list[MeasurementStationMetadata]]): List of measurement station metadata JSON document(s) according to the IEA Task 43 WRA Data Model, for all station datasets used in the EYA. Default is None. reference_wind_farms (Optional[list[ReferenceWindFarm]]): List of reference operational wind farms used in the EYA. Default is None. reference_meteorological_datasets (Optional[list[ReferenceMeteorologicalDataset]]): List of reference meteorological datasets used in the EYA. Default is None. wind_resource_assessments (Optional[list[WindResourceAssessment]]): List of wind resource assessments, including results, at the measurement station locations. Default is None. turbine_models (Optional[list[TurbineModel]]): List of wind turbine model specifications. Default is None. scenarios (Optional[list[Scenario]]): List of energy yield assessment scenarios. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_met_data.ReferenceMeteorologicalDataset
Metadata for a reference meteorological dataset.
The schema describes a dataset at a single horizontal spatial location. Separate data model instances need to be used to describe data at different location from the same source dataset (e.g. different grid cells from a reanalysis dataset).
Attributes: reference_meteorological_dataset_id (str): Unique ID for the reference meteorological dataset within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. location (Location): The horizontal spatial location of the meteorological data.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarm
Reference wind farm metadata.
Attributes: reference_wind_farm_id (str): Unique ID for the reference wind farm within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. wind_farm_configuration (WindFarmConfiguration): The configuration data for the reference wind farm. datasets (list[ReferenceWindFarmDataset]): Metadata for the operational dataset.

eya_def_tools.data_models.report_metadata.Organisation
Issuing or receiving organisation of an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Entity name of the organisation. abbreviation (Optional[str]): Abbreviated name of the organisation. Default is None. address (Optional[str]): Address of the organisation. Default is None. contact_name (Optional[str]): Name(s) of contact person(s) in the organisation. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.report_metadata.ReportContributor
Contributor to an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the contributor. email_address (Optional[EmailStr]): Email address of the contributor. Default is None. contributor_type (ReportContributorType(StrEnum)): Type of contributor. contribution_comments (Optional[str]): Comments to clarify contribution. Default is None. completion_date (Optional[date]): Contribution completion date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.CoordinateReferenceSystem
Specification of a coordinate reference system for GIS data.
Attributes: system_label (str): Label of the coordinate system. epsg_srid (Optional[int]): EPSG Spatial Reference System Identifier (SRID). Default is None. wkt (Optional[str]): Well-known text (WKT) string definition of the coordinate system. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.turbine_model.TurbineModel
Specification of a wind turbine model.
Attributes: turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. label (str): Label of the turbine model. perf_spec_ref (Optional[TurbineModelSpecification]): Reference to a json document with turbine model performance specification (PLACEHOLDER). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id (str): Unique ID of the wind resource assessment within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. wind_speed_results (list[Result]): Final long-term wind speed estimates from the wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.Location
Specification of a horizontal location in space.
Attributes: location_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the location. Default is None. label (Optional[str]): Label of the location. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. x (float): Location x-coordinate (typically easing). y (float): Location y-coordinate (typically northing).

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarmDataset
Reference wind farm operational dataset metadata.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the reference wind farm dataset. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. data_supplier_organisation (Organisation): The organisation that supplied the data. data_type (OperationalDataType(StrEnum)): The type of data in the operational data, categorised as 'scada' for data from a Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition (SCADA) system, 'metered' for data from a production meter, 'environmental_measurement' for data from an (on-site) environmental measurement station such as a meteorological mast or a remote sensing device (RSD) and 'other' for any other type of unit. data_source_type (DataSourceType(StrEnum)): The type of the operational data source. Primary data, such as primary SCADA data, comes directly from the source without processing. Report data refers to data extracted from report document, such as monthly operational reports. Other secondary data comprises all other data source categories, such as secondary SCADA data provided in processed (harmonised) form by a data management service provider. used_data_variables (list[ReferenceWindFarmDataVariable]): A list of the types of data variables included in this dataset and used in the assessment. For a large dataset (such as a full wind turbine SCADA dataset) this field should not include all the variables but only the ones that were used in the analysis. time_resolution (TimeResolution(StrEnum)): Time resolution of the data. data_period_start_date (date): Start of the data period in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD. data_period_end_date (date): End of the data period in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: name (str): Name of the wind farm. label (Optional[str]): Abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment. operational_lifetime_start_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime start date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. wind_farm_restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations.
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id_reference (str): The ID of the wind resource assessment on which the turbine wind resource assessment is based. This must refer to an ID of a wind resource assessment included at the top level of the EYA DEF. The schema requires that a turbine wind resource assessment is based on only one wind resource assessment. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. wind_spatial_modelling_processes (list[AssessmentProcessDescription]): Wind spatial modelling processes used in the assessment. wind_speed_results (list[Result]): Final long-term wind speed estimates at the turbine location(s). wind_uncertainty_categories (list[WindUncertaintyCategory]): Wind related uncertainty assessment categories including results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.plant_performance.PlantPerformanceSubcategoryElement
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory element.
Attributes: label (str): Label of the plant performance loss subcategory element. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance loss subcategory element assessment. The basis describes the level of detail of the calculation or estimate used in the assessment of the element. variability (TimeVariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in the plant performance loss subcategory element. is_independent (bool): Whether the plant performance loss subcategory element is independent of all other elements. Default is True. assessment_process_descriptions (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Description of calculation processes used in the assessment of the plant performance loss subcategory element. Default is None. element_results (list[Result]): Plant performance assessment subcategory element result(s) as dimensionless loss factors (efficiencies).

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarmDataVariable
Reference wind farm operational data variable metadata.
Attributes: label (str): Label of the data variable. This is currently free text but should be replaced by a list of enum options. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. data_level (OperationalDataLevel(StrEnum)): Whether the operational data variable is provided for each individual wind turbine ('turbine_level'), is aggregated at the wind farm level ('wind_farm_level') or corresponds to a different ('other') unit such as an environmental measurement station. statistic_types (list[StatisticType(StrEnum)]): A list of the types of statistics included for this data variable. measurement_point (Optional[str]): Optional clarification of the point of measurement, such as the location of the energy meter for metered production. Default is None. raw_data_recovery_rate (Optional[list[Result]]): Dimensionless raw data recovery rate for the variable. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.OperationalRestriction
Specifications of a restriction that limits power output.
In the current draft of the schema, 'label', 'description' and 'comments' fields are available to describe the restriction with free text. This is intended to be expanded into a more comprehensive data model.
Attributes: label (str): Short label to indicate the type of operational restriction. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.TurbineConfiguration
Specification of all details for a turbine configuration.
Attributes: turbine_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the turbine specification. Default is None. label (str): Label of the turbine. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. location (Location): The horizontal spatial location of the turbine. hub_height (float): The hub height of the turbine. turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the turbine level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_uncertainty.WindUncertaintySubcategory
